Package com.sun.xml.ws.security.policy

Interface AlgorithmSuite

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlgorithmSuite
    public interface AlgorithmSuite
    Represents the AlgorithmSuite assertion.

    Syntax : 

      <xmp>
  <sp:AlgorithmSuite ... >
      <wsp:Policy>
          (
          <sp:Basic256 ... /> |
          <sp:Basic192 ... /> |
          <sp:Basic128 ... /> |
          <sp:TripleDes ... /> |
          <sp:Basic256Rsa15 ... /> |
          <sp:Basic192Rsa15 ... /> |
          <sp:Basic128Rsa15 ... /> |
          <sp:TripleDesRsa15 ... /> |
          <sp:Basic256Sha256 ... /> |
          <sp:Basic192Sha256 ... /> |
          <sp:Basic128Sha256 ... /> |
          <sp:TripleDesSha256 ... /> |
          <sp:Basic256Sha256Rsa15 ... /> |
          <sp:Basic192Sha256Rsa15 ... /> |
          <sp:Basic128Sha256Rsa15 ... /> |
          <sp:TripleDesSha256Rsa15 ... /> |

           ...)
          <sp:InclusiveC14N ... /> ?
          <sp:SOAPNormalization10 ... /> ?
          <sp:STRTransform10 ... /> ?
          <sp:XPath10 ... /> ?
          <sp:XPathFilter20 ... /> ?
          ...
      </wsp:Policy>
    ...
   </sp:AlgorithmSuite>
 </xmp>
    Author:
    K.Venugopal@sun.com
